Package: sandrocoind
Architecture: any
Depends: +ACQAew-shlibs:Depends+AH0-, +ACQAew-misc:Depends+AH0-
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - daemon
 Sandrocoin is an experimental new digital currency that enables instant
 payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. Sandrocoin uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Sandrocoin Core
 is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides the daemon, sandrocoind, and the CLI tool
 sandrocoin-cli to interact with the daemon.

